{"tid":1666002,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"10月20，旺角之後，有一事發現","createTime":"2019-10-20T19:27:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T03:32:39.000Z","uid":157886,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5396f26ae0a0e419471a356e7f422dca1e79fa41","tid":1666002,"uid":157886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T19:27:10.000Z","msg":"今日夜晚大約10點，見到有直升機，果時已經心知不妙，同身邊既人講要走啦，佢知道曬我地係邊，但無人理！算，咁我咪同我班teammate 一齊走，走到半路，真係有畜生出左黎，仲要包抄彌敦道，後尾聽到有至少10個手足俾狗咬到！<br />\n<br />\n我想講下次可唔可以一出直升機就走，佢可以高空監察我地，仲可以知點包我地！我地就只可以企係到俾人捉<br />\n<br />\n最後，光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"65b117cecef595cfb7d0f4acdbffcc04f6688728","tid":1666002,"uid":157886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T19:27:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"91647219c9fd388632c4dd3ae41c5781413b8f1a","tid":1666002,"uid":235025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T19:28:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c021bea33c46d9bbb4175d2ea4a02bd499eddb99","tid":1666002,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T19:29:04.000Z","msg":"佢出得就一定係預備捉人 <br />\n<br />\n有時出咗好耐都冇捉 係嗰陣時難捉"},{"pid":"8ae618c99cb670e425d79733255359815f5d2ddc","tid":1666002,"uid":109820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T19:31:07.000Z","msg":"分化撚 失敗撚 中計撚 全！面！進！場！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666001\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666001</a>"},{"pid":"8d96309d671e8dc0b723134a8acfe3283316618a","tid":1666002,"uid":136893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T19:31:51.000Z","msg":"入黎睇下有無認得既手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n救手足啊，幫手推推<br />\n留意comment 同picture 戈到仲有update ga，唔係淨係得一樓有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個po 起碼有100up手足等緊你救<br />\n已知身份同已搵律師既唔超過10個<br />\n救人啊大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n10.20被捕人士整合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg